# Operation Frontier / NoetherSolve — generated outputs (dashboard + charts regenerate from tsv)
experiments/operation_frontier/results/dashboard.html
experiments/operation_frontier/results/charts/
experiments/operation_frontier/results/hunt_results.json
# Open questions queue — local state, regenerates from autonomy_loop.py
